@startuml Immediate Transfer Flow with Smart Rate Handling
title Immediate Transfer Sequence Diagram (v2 - Smart Rate Handling)
participant User as U
participant Frontend as FE
participant Backend as API
participant Supabase as DB
participant Chimoney as CHI

autonumber

== 1. TRANSFER INITIATION ==

U -> FE: Opens "Send Money" screen
activate FE

FE -> API: GET /api/beneficiaries/list\n(X-User-Id: user_uuid)
activate API
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM beneficiaries\nWHERE user_id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: List of saved beneficiaries
deactivate DB
API --> FE: { beneficiaries: [...] }
deactivate API

FE -> FE: Display beneficiary list\nfor selection

U -> FE: Selects beneficiary (Amit Kumar)
FE -> FE: Shows selected beneficiary details

U -> FE: Enters amount: $500 USD
FE -> FE: Validate amount\n($10 - $50,000)

== 2. GET EXCHANGE RATE ==

FE -> API: GET /api/transfers/exchange-rate?\namount=500&source=USD&target=INR
activate API

API -> CHI: GET /v0.2.4/payouts/rates\n?countryTo=IN
activate CHI
CHI --> API: { rates: { USD: { rate: 83.25 } } }
deactivate CHI

API -> API: Calculate amounts\n500 USD × 83.25 = 41,625 INR\nFee: $2.50\nTotal: $502.50

API --> FE: {\n  exchange_rate: 83.25,\n  target_amount: 41625,\n  fee_amount: 2.50,\n  expires_at: now + 30s,\n  is_locked: false\n}
deactivate API

FE -> FE: Display rate breakdown:\n- You send: $502.50\n- Recipient gets: ₹41,625\n- Rate: 1 USD = ₹83.25\n- Countdown: 30s ⏱️

== 3. USER CONFIRMS DETAILS ==

U -> FE: Clicks "Confirm & Review"
FE -> FE: Move to review screen\nShow all details with\n"Cannot be reversed" warning

U -> FE: Clicks "Confirm & Send"
FE -> FE: Show loading spinner

== 4. TRANSFER INITIATION (Create Record) ==

FE -> API: POST /api/transfers/initiate\nAuthorization: Bearer token\nX-User-Id: user_uuid\n{\n  beneficiary_id: "abc-123",\n  source_amount: 502.50,\n  exchange_rate: 83.25,\n  target_amount: 41625,\n  fee_amount: 2.50\n}
activate API

API -> API: Validate authorization\nValidate amount, beneficiary

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfers (\n  user_id, beneficiary_id,\n  source_amount, target_amount,\n  exchange_rate: 83.25,\n  status: 'pending'\n)
activate DB
DB --> API: transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789"
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfer_status_log (\n  transfer_id, old_status: NULL,\n  new_status: 'pending'\n)
deactivate DB

API --> FE: {\n  success: true,\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789",\n  status: "pending"\n}
deactivate API

== 5. TRANSFER EXECUTION (Send to Chimoney) ==

FE -> API: POST /api/transfers/execute\nAuthorization: Bearer token\nX-User-Id: user_uuid\n{\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789"\n}
activate API

API -> API: BEGIN TRANSACTION

note over API: ✅ SMART RATE CHECK\n(Favor user when possible)

API -> CHI: GET /v0.2.4/payouts/rates\n(Re-check CURRENT rate)
activate CHI
CHI --> API: Current rate: ?
deactivate CHI

API -> API: Compare rates:\nOriginal: 83.25\nCurrent: ??

alt Rate became BETTER (favorable)
  note over API: 🎉 User gets MORE money\nRate: 83.25 → 83.50\nAmount: 41,625 → 41,750\n✅ Accept silently (no alert)

  API -> API: Update transfer\noriginal_rate: 83.25\nfinal_rate: 83.50\nfinal_amount: 41,750\nrate_improved: true

else Rate became WORSE (unfavorable) AND change > 1%
  note over API: ⚠️ User gets LESS money\nRate: 83.25 → 83.00\nAmount: 41,625 → 41,500\n🚨 ALERT USER FOR CONFIRMATION

  API --> FE: {\n  error_code: 'RATE_CHANGED',\n  old_rate: 83.25,\n  new_rate: 83.00,\n  old_amount: 41625,\n  new_amount: 41500,\n  difference_percent: -0.30%,\n  requires_confirmation: true\n}
  deactivate API

  FE -> FE: Show RateChangeModal:\n"Exchange rate dropped"\n"Old: ₹83.25 (₹41,625)"\n"New: ₹83.00 (₹41,500)"\n[Accept New Rate] [Go Back]

  alt User clicks "Accept New Rate"
    U -> FE: Accepts new rate

    FE -> API: POST /api/transfers/execute\n(RETRY with accept_rate_change: true)
    activate API

    API -> API: Update transfer with new rate\nfinal_rate: 83.00\nfinal_amount: 41500\nrate_worsened: true\nuser_confirmed: true

  else User clicks "Go Back"
    U -> FE: Cancels
    FE -> FE: Return to review screen

    API --> FE: { cancelled: true }
    deactivate API

    note over FE: User can:\n1. Adjust amount\n2. Try again\n3. Cancel transfer
  end

else Rate became WORSE BUT change ≤ 1%
  note over API: Rate changed but ≤1%\nRate: 83.25 → 83.15 (-0.12%)\n✅ Accept silently\n(Minor change, not worth alerting)

  API -> API: Update transfer\noriginal_rate: 83.25\nfinal_rate: 83.15\nfinal_amount: 41,575\nrate_slightly_worse: true

end

== 6. FINALIZE TRANSFER (If Rate Accepted) ==

API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
API -> DB: UPDATE transfers\nSET status = 'processing'
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfer_status_log (\n  transfer_id, new_status: 'processing'\n)
deactivate DB

note over API: Get beneficiary details\nfrom database

API -> DB: SELECT beneficiaries\nWHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: Beneficiary data
deactivate DB

API -> CHI: POST /v0.2.4/payouts/bank\nHeaders: X-API-Key: chimoney_key\n{\n  amount: 500,\n  account_number: "...",\n  bank_code: "HDFC0000123",\n  fullname: "Amit Kumar"\n}
activate CHI

note over CHI: Chimoney validates\nProcesses transfer\nReturns transaction ID

CHI --> API: {\n  success: true,\n  id: "chi_9876543210"\n}
deactivate CHI

API -> DB: UPDATE transfers\nSET\n  status = 'processing',\n  chimoney_transaction_id = 'chi_9876543210',\n  final_exchange_rate = 83.00,\n  final_target_amount = 41500,\n  executed_at = NOW()\nWHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
deactivate DB

API --> FE: {\n  success: true,\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789",\n  status: "processing",\n  chimoney_transaction_id: "chi_9876543210",\n  final_exchange_rate: 83.00,\n  final_target_amount: 41500,\n  executed_at: "2026-02-28T12:46:00Z"\n}
deactivate API

== 7. SHOW CONFIRMATION RECEIPT ==

FE -> FE: Hide loading spinner
FE -> FE: Show confirmation screen with:\n- Transaction ID\n- Final amounts (with rate change if any)\n- Recipient: Amit Kumar (UPI)\n- Amount sent: $502.50\n- Amount received: ₹41,500\n- Status: Processing (2-5 min)\n- ℹ️ Rate changed during processing\n  From: ₹83.25 → To: ₹83.00

U -> FE: Views receipt / Shares / Done

note over DB,CHI: Chimoney processes transfer\nin background (2-5 minutes)\nWill send webhook when completed\n(Future enhancement)

@enduml
